(HOUSE MUSIC PLAYING)

31:28.387 --> 31:29.488
You're kidding, right?

31:32.391 --> 31:34.160
Shaun, you know,
you don't have to...

31:34.293 --> 31:36.028
You don't have to, uh...
You don't have to do this.

31:36.162 --> 31:37.229
We can go to dinner
at the...

31:37.363 --> 31:39.065
Wh-where do you
get the linguini?

31:39.198 --> 31:40.299
ASHER: Yeah. Where...

31:40.432 --> 31:43.335
****

31:44.570 --> 31:47.339
(NEON BUZZING)

31:55.047 --> 31:57.349
****

32:02.221 --> 32:04.356
Intermittent photothermic
laser light therapy.

32:06.225 --> 32:07.426
We've gotta go back!

32:07.559 --> 32:08.360
Okay!

32:09.028 --> 32:11.030
****

32:19.438 --> 32:20.606
I scared.

32:21.840 --> 32:23.342
I am confident.

32:23.475 --> 32:25.677
Using a laser combined
with chemical thrombolysis

32:25.811 --> 32:27.879
to break up
the clot in your...

32:30.582 --> 32:32.484
(INHALES DEEPLY)

32:32.618 --> 32:35.387
****

32:39.225 --> 32:40.226
Lo se.

32:58.610 --> 33:00.612
****

33:09.121 --> 33:10.922
I had the operation?

33:11.757 --> 33:14.426
Si. Salio de maravilla.

33:15.694 --> 33:18.097
The tumor is gone?

33:19.165 --> 33:20.199
Adios, tumor.

33:22.101 --> 33:28.740
Muy pronto
vas a estar marcando
contra el portero.

33:28.874 --> 33:31.610
****

33:33.945 --> 33:35.681
(CHUCKLES)

33:47.959 --> 33:49.161
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

33:54.633 --> 33:55.701
Do you remember
when we first met?

33:58.304 --> 34:00.005
I was very wet.

34:00.139 --> 34:02.474
Yeah, and you saved
that little boy's life
that day too.

34:04.143 --> 34:05.544
Why are you crying?

34:05.677 --> 34:07.346
(SIGHS)

34:07.479 --> 34:09.047
Because I'm so happy.

34:12.184 --> 34:13.852
And I'm a little bit sad.

34:13.985 --> 34:16.955
How can you be
happy and sad
at the same time?

34:20.326 --> 34:21.260
Well, I'm happy for you.

34:22.528 --> 34:24.096
For how far you've come

34:25.364 --> 34:26.532
and for the joy
you've found,

34:30.169 --> 34:31.770
the amazing man
you've become.

34:31.903 --> 34:34.406
****

34:38.344 --> 34:39.811
And I'm sad
because I miss you.

34:44.716 --> 34:46.185
I miss you, too.

34:48.987 --> 34:49.888
Oh.

34:59.565 --> 35:00.932
Oh. I need to go.

35:02.768 --> 35:06.104
Oh. Shaun, you gotta
get married in...

35:07.673 --> 35:09.341
Five hours!

35:09.475 --> 35:11.543
I'm getting married
in five hours.

35:12.811 --> 35:15.013
Wha... What are you
gonna wear?

35:15.147 --> 35:16.382
I don't know.

35:19.084 --> 35:20.386
(CHUCKLES)

35:25.391 --> 35:27.559
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

35:27.693 --> 35:30.562
****

35:36.235 --> 35:38.069
Don't look yet.

35:38.204 --> 35:42.073
I just need to flare out
the veil a little more.

35:42.208 --> 35:43.875
And voila.

35:45.076 --> 35:48.947
****

35:49.080 --> 35:49.881
Oh!

35:51.517 --> 35:53.151
Meghan Markle
is so jealous right now.

35:53.285 --> 35:54.420
(CHUCKLES)

36:01.927 --> 36:04.196
(EXHALES SHAKILY)

36:04.330 --> 36:05.964
They're the most adorable
couple ever.

36:06.097 --> 36:08.634
Well, maybe second.

36:08.767 --> 36:11.002
And what I really
admire about them

36:11.136 --> 36:14.673
is that they
respect each other
for who they are.

36:14.806 --> 36:17.476
Mm.
Accept each other
as individuals.

36:17.609 --> 36:19.945
There. I canceled
the bread maker.

36:20.078 --> 36:21.513
What do you want
to get them?

36:21.647 --> 36:23.148
Ah, something that
represents us.

36:23.282 --> 36:24.316
Marriage counseling?

36:24.450 --> 36:26.618
Perfect.

36:26.752 --> 36:29.154
I've been totally shipping
Shaun and Lea.

36:29.288 --> 36:31.323
Hashtag She-Ea.

36:31.457 --> 36:35.160
Hashtag Le-Ash.

36:35.294 --> 36:38.730
Uh, that spells "leash,"
so, no.

36:38.864 --> 36:40.031
Ah.

36:40.165 --> 36:42.033
Oh, I should explain
about the matching suits.

36:42.167 --> 36:44.970
For the record,
I think they're fabulous

36:45.103 --> 36:46.305
and we look great
in them.

36:47.773 --> 36:49.174
Thank you for saying that.

36:49.308 --> 36:52.611
We look like
a couple of dorks.

36:52.744 --> 36:54.346
I was wrong about
the matchy-matchy vibe.

36:54.480 --> 36:55.781
I'm sorry.

36:55.914 --> 36:59.184
Ah, I love a man
who can admit
when he's wrong.

36:59.318 --> 37:01.653
And I may
look like a dork,
but I'm his dork.

37:02.954 --> 37:04.656
And he's mine.
Mm.

37:04.790 --> 37:06.658
****

37:14.132 --> 37:15.066
Wow.

37:15.200 --> 37:16.368
You look great.

37:16.502 --> 37:19.204
I kept trying.

37:19.338 --> 37:22.040
Last night, I wore it
for two minutes,

37:22.173 --> 37:24.075
and then five,
and then ten.

37:24.209 --> 37:26.244
I got up to
44 minutes.

37:29.014 --> 37:31.182
So, 44 minutes
is your max, huh?

37:31.317 --> 37:32.618
Yes.

37:32.751 --> 37:35.687
Weddings don't run like
a Swiss watch, you know?

37:35.821 --> 37:38.189
I timed the service
at 42 minutes

37:38.324 --> 37:40.792
if I skip
the redundant parts
of my vows

37:40.926 --> 37:42.694
and exit the church
with Lea very quickly.

37:44.863 --> 37:47.433
I covered the "In sickness
and in health" part

37:47.566 --> 37:48.900
in my Hippocratic Oath.

37:49.034 --> 37:51.102
Let's hope the flower girl
keeps up the pace, huh?

37:51.236 --> 37:52.170
(EXHALES DEEPLY)
Oh, yes.

37:53.204 --> 37:54.373
(KNOCK AT DOOR)

37:54.506 --> 37:56.542
****

37:58.777 --> 37:59.778
(EXHALES DEEPLY)
You ready?

38:02.348 --> 38:03.415
I'm ready.

38:05.216 --> 38:06.151
Yeah, you are.

38:11.557 --> 38:12.858
We need to talk.

38:12.991 --> 38:16.395
****

38:37.583 --> 38:38.817
I'm not accepting
your resignation.

38:40.486 --> 38:41.820
That's very nice
of you, but...

38:44.255 --> 38:45.491
I can't.

38:45.624 --> 38:46.758
Well, not on your own.

38:48.527 --> 38:49.795
That's why I want you
to come stay with me.

38:50.896 --> 38:51.997
With my boss?

38:53.765 --> 38:54.833
With your friend.

38:59.304 --> 39:00.706
Please say yes.

39:00.839 --> 39:03.775
****

39:23.629 --> 39:24.830
(SIGHS)

39:30.101 --> 39:31.837
You look so handsome.

39:33.639 --> 39:35.306
You look so beautiful.

39:35.441 --> 39:36.708
(CHUCKLES)

39:36.842 --> 39:38.410
Gosling and Markle.

39:39.945 --> 39:41.980
But not Shaun and Lea.

39:45.551 --> 39:46.818
I am so sorry, Shaun.

39:48.253 --> 39:50.789
I knew the world
would be seeing us,

39:50.922 --> 39:52.824
and I wanted to show everyone
how amazing you are

39:52.958 --> 39:55.060
and how good it is to be
in a relationship with you.

39:55.193 --> 39:58.363
But...you're so uncomfortable,
aren't you?

39:58.497 --> 40:01.533
I can only last for
another 39 minutes.

40:01.667 --> 40:05.336
I love you so much
for putting yourself
through this.

40:05.471 --> 40:08.339
But we shouldn't have to.

40:10.341 --> 40:13.078
I can't wait
to marry you.

40:14.646 --> 40:15.847
But not like this.

40:20.652 --> 40:21.720
Yes.

40:22.888 --> 40:24.155
Not like this.

40:25.524 --> 40:26.525
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

40:27.292 --> 40:28.259
(DOOR OPENS)

40:29.360 --> 40:30.228
Everything okay?

40:30.361 --> 40:31.563
Yes.

40:33.364 --> 40:35.233
But there's not
gonna be a wedding.

40:35.366 --> 40:36.367
Oh.

40:36.502 --> 40:38.303
Not today.

40:38.436 --> 40:40.405
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

40:40.539 --> 40:43.241
I'm so sorry.
We ruined your show.

40:43.374 --> 40:45.310
Wedding show
without a wedding.

40:45.443 --> 40:47.078
Yeah, pretty much.

40:47.212 --> 40:48.880
I thought this was bigger
than Shaun and me,

40:49.014 --> 40:49.948
but it shouldn't be.

40:51.583 --> 40:55.120
It's our day,
and this just isn't us.

40:59.390 --> 41:01.192
Couldn't have
figured this out
45 minutes from now?

41:01.326 --> 41:02.694
I know.

41:03.695 --> 41:05.664
****

41:05.797 --> 41:08.099
Go be happy.
Go be you.

41:09.935 --> 41:10.902
Oh.
Oh!

41:11.036 --> 41:11.903
Thank you!

41:12.904 --> 41:14.072
Okay. Oh!

41:17.709 --> 41:18.910
Hell of a twist.

41:21.680 --> 41:23.248
You heading back
tomorrow?

41:23.381 --> 41:25.216
The cases will be
piling up.

41:25.350 --> 41:26.652
Hm.

41:26.785 --> 41:27.919
You should take the job.

41:29.688 --> 41:31.122
You'd make
a fantastic chief.

41:33.024 --> 41:34.926
I don't know
about fantastic.

41:35.060 --> 41:36.094
I do.

41:37.395 --> 41:38.630
You made me
a better one.

41:41.132 --> 41:42.200
(SIGHS)
(CHUCKLES)

41:42.333 --> 41:44.803
****

41:46.271 --> 41:47.272
We're losing

41:47.405 --> 41:48.439
serious points, aren't we?

41:48.574 --> 41:50.108
(CHUCKLES) So many.

41:56.214 --> 41:58.950
****

